- The integer array parameter `sentences` must not be null.
- The length of the integer array parameter `sentences` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- The length of each string in the integer array parameter `sentences` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- Each string in the integer array parameter `sentences` consists only of lowercase English letters and spaces.
- Each string in the integer array parameter `sentences` does not have leading or trailing spaces.
- All words in each string in the integer array parameter `sentences` are separated by a single space.
- The integer result is the maximum number of words that appear in a single sentence.